      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，axisFormat用%ms。分区方面：P1对应HelmChart，P2和P3都是Serverless场景，最后单独一个Llegadas区放所有到达里程碑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart",
        "P2",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "P3",
        "Llegadas"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，基础结构有了。P1区我先放T1_exec，0到4毫秒，标记为active状态；然后T1_IO是6到9毫秒，这个IO操作标为crit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_IO",
        "active",
        "crit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "P1的T1_IO为什么是6开始？中间2到6毫秒是空闲吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_IO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，P1在4毫秒执行完后有2毫秒间隔，然后才触发IO。P2这边T1_exec接在P1后面，4到8毫秒，也是active。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P2还需要T2_exec，12到14毫秒，然后紧跟着T2_IO到16毫秒。P3的T1_exec和P2-T2_ULT可以并行，都是8到12毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_exec",
        "P2-T2_IO",
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P3-T2_ULT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上。P2-T2_IO标为crit，P3-T2_ULT用done状态表示已完成。现在处理Llegadas区的里程碑：P1_arrive在0毫秒，P2-T1_arrive在1毫秒，P3-T1_arrive在2毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
