      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，P2-T2_arrive是3毫秒还是4毫秒？我记混了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_arrive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "确认一下：P2-T2_arrive是3毫秒，P3-T2_arrive才是4毫秒。最后P3-T3_arrive在5毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_arrive",
